OL,3,CStack faces legal challenge as
OL,4,CNewcastle pubs fear they are at
OL,5,C'serious risk'
OL,7,FAn alliance of more than 100 Newcastle
OL,8,Fbars and pubs has mounted a legal
OL,9,Fchallenge against the Stack fanzone
OL,10,Foutside St James' Park.
OL,12,FEarlier this summer, the 2,000-
OL,13,Fcapacity venue was granted a five-year
OL,14,Fextension to its planning permission
OL,15,Fby Newcastle City Council.
OL,17,FBut city centre businesses, uniting
OL,18,Funder the banner of the newly-formed
OL,19,FNE1 Hospitality Group, are now trying
OL,20,Fto get the decision quashed.
