OL,3,CStack faces legal challenge as
OL,4,CNewcastle pubs fear they are at
OL,5,C'serious risk'
OL,7,FThey claim that the St James' Stack,
OL,8,Fwhich opened in 2024 and now has
OL,9,Fapproval to keep running until 2031,
OL,10,Fis endangering the city's nightlife.
OL,12,FThe group said that soaring footfall
OL,13,Fat the Stack, throughout the week and
OL,14,Fnot just on Newcastle United
OL,15,Fmatchdays, is taking trade away from
OL,16,Fother venues and putting jobs "at
OL,17,Fserious risk" at a time when the
OL,18,Fhospitality industry is struggling.
OL,26,@xD@_OUyD@MO]
