OL,3,CStack faces legal challenge as
OL,4,CNewcastle pubs fear they are at
OL,5,C'serious risk'
OL,7,FAn application has been made for a
OL,8,FHigh Court judicial review of the
OL,9,Fcouncil's decision to extend the
OL,10,Fplanning permission, which the NE1
OL,11,FHospitality Group believe is
OL,12,F"unlawful".
OL,14,FJudicial reviews can only be used to
OL,15,Fchallenge the legality of a planning
OL,16,Fdecision that has been made, not the
OL,17,Fmerits of the application in question.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@JO]
