OL,3,CStack faces legal challenge as
OL,4,CNewcastle pubs fear they are at
OL,5,C'serious risk'
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the alliance said
OL,8,Fon Tuesday night: "This isn't about
OL,9,Fgrowth ` it's about displacement. The
OL,10,FFanzone is drawing trade away from the
OL,11,Fvery venues that helped build
OL,12,FNewcastle's reputation for
OL,13,Fhospitality. We're not against
OL,14,Fprogress but it must be fair and
OL,15,Fsustainable.
OL,17,F"Several major venues have already
OL,18,Fclosed this year. Investment is drying
OL,19,Fup. Jobs are under threat. And the
OL,20,Fcouncil seems unwilling to listen.
OL,26,@pD@SOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/13
