OL,5,C'serious risk'
OL,7,F"This Judicial Review is a last
OL,8,Fresort, but we cannot allow the voices
OL,9,Fof local businesses to be drowned out.
OL,10,FWe intend to seek an order to quash
OL,11,Fthe decision as we have been advised
OL,12,Fthat it is unlawful.
OL,14,F"However, we would wish to negotiate
OL,15,Fan outcome acceptable to all which
OL,16,Fwould avoid continuing these
OL,17,Fproceedings. The sooner that we can do
OL,18,Fthis the better it will be for all
OL,19,Fconcerned, both now and in the long
OL,20,Frun."
