OL,3,CStack faces legal challenge as
OL,4,CNewcastle pubs fear they are at
OL,5,C'serious risk'
OL,7,FTommy Byron, of the Dog and Parrot bar
OL,8,Fon Clayton Street West, added: "I'm a
OL,9,FGeordie through and through and have
OL,10,Ffollowed Newcastle since I was a
OL,11,Fbairn. I want to celebrate the club's
OL,12,Fsuccess ` but right now we're fighting
OL,13,Ffor survival. We're asking the council
OL,14,Fto think long-term, to support the
OL,15,Flocal businesses and communities that
OL,16,Fmake this city unique."
