OL,3,CStack faces legal challenge as
OL,4,CNewcastle pubs fear they are at
OL,5,C'serious risk'
OL,7,FVaulkhard Group boss Ollie Vaulkhard,
OL,8,Fwhose venues include the Town Wall and
OL,9,FBridge Tavern pubs, said his business
OL,10,Fwas suffering "a steady erosion of
OL,11,Fincome" and that "growth should
OL,12,Fbenefit the whole city, not just one
OL,13,Fmega-venue".
OL,15,FThere are 175 people employed at
OL,16,FStack, which is built from 56
OL,17,Frepurposed shipping containers, and
OL,18,Fmore than 1,400 stage performances
OL,19,Fhave been held there since its launch.
