OL,5,C'serious risk'
OL,7,FThe venue welcomed 35,000 patrons
OL,8,Fduring Sam Fender's concerts at St
OL,9,FJames' Park this summer, around a
OL,10,Ffifth of the total number of people
OL,11,Fwho attended the three gigs.
OL,13,FNewcastle City Council said that it
OL,14,Fwanted to "work with businesses to
OL,15,Fensure Newcastle continues to thrive
OL,16,Fas a hub for hospitality".
