OL,7,FA spokesperson for the authority
OL,8,Fadded: "We understand that recent
OL,9,Fyears have been difficult for
OL,10,Fbusinesses, in hospitality and
OL,11,Felsewhere, both here and in other
OL,12,Ftowns and cities across the country.
OL,14,F"While we have seen some operators
OL,15,Fsadly close their doors, other new
OL,16,Fbusinesses have opened in Newcastle
OL,17,Fand are flourishing, adding to the
OL,18,Foffer in the city centre and beyond.
OL,26,@pD@HOU
