OL,3,CStack faces legal challenge as
OL,4,CNewcastle pubs fear they are at
OL,5,C'serious risk'
OL,7,F"We had agreed to meet a number of
OL,8,Fbusinesses who had raised concerns
OL,9,Faround pressures on the hospitality
OL,10,Findustry, we recognise the concerns
OL,11,Fand want to work together.
OL,13,F"Prior to that meeting taking place we
OL,14,Fbecame aware that some of those
OL,15,Fbusinesses were planning to submit a
OL,16,Fjudicial review to challenge the
OL,17,Fdecision to extend the time limit for
OL,18,Fthe STACK. As a result of these legal
OL,19,Fproceedings, which we would not be
OL,20,Fable to address in any meeting, it was
OL,21,Fpostponed.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
