OL,7,F"While we understand and recognise the
OL,8,Fconcerns raised, as a council, we
OL,9,Fcannot regulate competition in the
OL,10,Fcity centre and that would not be
OL,11,Fgrounds to refuse a planning
OL,12,Fapplication."
OL,14,FStack and Newcastle United did not
OL,15,Fwish to comment.
